When working in AiNative or repos using this OS:

- Architecture spec: `ENGINEERING-OS.md`
- PR review: follow `docs/systems/pr-review-system.md`; prompts in `docs/ai-workflows/pr-review-prompts.md`
- Task grooming / meetings: `docs/ai-workflows/task-grooming-prompts.md`
- Multi-file features: use `docs/ai-workflows/coordinator-worker.md` (Research → Plan → Execute)
- Commands and setup: `docs/reference/` — navigate by domain, do not guess
- After hard bugs: append to `docs/debugging/<domain>/` using `docs/debugging/template.md`
- Significant decisions: new ADR in `docs/decisions/` using `docs/decisions/template.md`
- Raw capture during work: write to `scratch/` (gitignored); promote on Friday review

Commits: Conventional Commits, short messages (see Commit-style rule).
